The Fleet Air Arm Officers Association

The Fleet Air Arm Officers Association is a thriving organisation whose serving and retired members want to keep in touch, keep informed about today's Fleet Air Arm and keep alive the unique comradeship, professionalism and can-do spirit epitomised by the Fleet Air Arm.

This website provides a focal point for anyone seeking information about the Fleet Air Arm. A comprehensive heritage section is continually being expanded. Galleries show the Fleet Air Arm in action around the world and regularly updated news items inform public and members alike what today's Fleet Air Arm is doing.

The exclusive, secure members area has contact details for all members. Members must log in to view member-only news items, events, reunions, meetings, lectures and to change their contact details.
